{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "萧十一郎在偏僻小客栈照顾昏迷三天的沈璧君。沈璧君醒来后与萧十一郎对话，谈及小公子的可怕和萧十一郎的名声，沈璧君表示若遇萧十一郎定要杀他。沈家庄老家丁沈义突然到来要接沈璧君回去，萧十一郎识破沈义已被小公子收买，暴打沈义并将其赶走。沈璧君大怒，醉酒后大闹客栈，辱骂萧十一郎，声称他是强盗，甚至咬伤他的手。萧十一郎内心充满矛盾，既想不再管她，又放不下对她的关心，最终决定无论她怎样都不能不救她。沈璧君自己雇车回沈家庄，途中梦见萧十一郎变成连城璧，满身鲜血。到达沈家庄后，她发现庄子已被烧成一片平地，人死伤散尽，彻底崩溃。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这次又是你救了我。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我自顾尚且不暇，哪里还有救人的本事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你又何必再瞒我，我知道上次也是你从她手中将我救出来的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "她？她是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你自然知道，就是那……那可怕的小公子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "大大小小的公子，我一个也不认得。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "但她却一定认得你，而且还很怕你，所以她虽然知道我在那山神庙，自己也不敢去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "她为什么要怕我？我这人难道很可怕吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "可怕的只是那些伪君子，我实在看错人了，也错怪了你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "像你这种人，本就不该出来走江湖的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你懂得的事太少，说的话却太多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你哼的是什么歌？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你说奇不奇怪，有人居然认为你是萧十一郎。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你难道从未听说过他做的那些事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你对他做的事难道知道的很多？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我只要知道一件就够了，他做的事无论哪一件都该砍头！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你也想砍他的头？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我若能遇见他，绝不会再让他活下去害人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你若遇见他，活不下去的只怕是你自己吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "沈义",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "借问大哥，连家的少夫人可是住在这里么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_shen_yi",
      "text": "是沈义吗？我就在这里，快进来。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "沈义",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "老奴不知小姐在这里受苦，迎接来迟，但望小姐恕罪。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_shen_yi",
      "text": "你来了就好，太夫人呢？她老人家可知道？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "沈义",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "小姐遇难的消息，早已传遍江湖，太夫人知道后，立刻令老奴等四处打听，今日才偶然听到这里的店伙说，他们这里有位女客人，病得很重，可是长得却如同天仙一样，老奴立刻就猜到他说的可能就是小姐了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "沈义",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "好在苍天有眼，总算让老奴找到了小姐，太夫人若是知道，也必定欢喜得很……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "沈义",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "小姐的伤势不要紧吧？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_shen_yi",
      "text": "现在已好多了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "沈义",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "既是如此，就请小姐快回去吧，也免得太夫人担心。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_shen_yi",
      "text": "现在……不太晚了么？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "沈义",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "秋天的日子短，其实此刻刚到戌时，何况老奴早已为小姐备好了车马。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_shen_yi",
      "text": "这位就是我的救命恩人，你快去为我叩谢他的大恩。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "沈义",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "多谢公子相救之德，沈家庄上上下下感同身受。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_yi",
      "text": "你是沈家庄的人？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "沈义",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "老奴侍候太夫人已有四十多年了，公子……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你这是干什么？他的确是我们家的人，你为何要如此对他？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_yi",
      "text": "回去告诉要你来的人，叫他要来就自己来，我等着他！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_yi",
      "speaker_name": "沈义",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "是太夫人要我来的，你凭什么打人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_yi",
      "text": "你这种人杀了也不过分，何况打；你若还不快滚，我就真宰了你。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "沈义在我们家工作了四十多年，始终忠心耿耿，你难道认为他也是别人派来害我的吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你救了我，我终生都感激，但你为什么定要留我在这里呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我并没有这个意思。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "那么，你这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你难道认为我对你有恶意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你若对我没有恶意，就请你现在送我回去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "现在还不行。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你究竟要等到什么时候才肯送我回去？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "也许再等三五天吧……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "等一等，话还没有说完，你不能走。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "店家……店小二……快来，快来……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "姑娘有什么吩咐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "快去替我雇辆车，我要回去，快，快……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "现在只怕雇不到车子。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "你去替我想法子，随你多少钱我都出。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "客官，真的要雇车么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "我要回去是我的事，和他有什么关系？你为何要问他？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你喝醉了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "谁说我喝醉了，我喝这么点酒就会醉么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "快去替我雇车，莫要理他，他自己才喝醉了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你不肯送我回去，为什么也不让我自己回去？你是我的什么人？凭什么要管我的事？凭什么要留住我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你真醉了，好好歇着吧，有什么话明天再说好不好？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈壁君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不行，我现在就要走。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你现在不能走。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你凭什么强迫我？你救过我，就想把我看成你的人了么？你再也休想，我根本不要你救，你若不放我走，不如杀了我吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "救命呀，这人是强盗，快去叫官兵来抓他……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我本还以为你是个好人，原来你也和那些人一样，救我也是有企图的，原来你比他们还可恶！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "那人可真蛮不讲理，是不是？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "是，是是是。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "我本不愿和这种人争吵的，但他实在太可恶了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "是是是。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "你知不知道大明湖旁边有个沈家庄？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这周围几百里地的人，谁不知道沈家庄？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "你知道我是谁么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "姑娘这还是第一次照顾小店的生意，下次再来小人就认得了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "告诉你，我就是沈家庄的沈姑娘，你若能在今天晚上送我回沈家庄，必定重重有赏。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "你不相信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "姑娘若真是沈家庄的人，只怕是回不去的了。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "沈家庄已被烧成了一片平地，庄子里的人有的死，有的伤，有的走得不知去向，现在连一个留下来的都没有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "我不信，你说的话我一个字也不相信。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "小人怎敢骗姑娘？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "你和他串通好了来骗我的，你们都不是好人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "姑娘若不相信，我也没法子……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "好，姑娘若是定要到沈家庄去瞧瞧，小人就陪姑娘走一趟吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人一定是个酒鬼，疯子！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 507
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "姑娘醒醒，沈家庄已到了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这里就是沈家庄，姑娘是不是要下车……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "我当然要下车，既已到家了，为什么不下车？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 563
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "其实……姑娘还是莫要下车的好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    }
